## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing (automated via browser subagent)

1. Open `http://localhost:8080/services/webasto-diagnostika` — verify hero, form, 5-step process, map render correctly
2. Open `http://localhost:8080/services/webasto-sumptomid` — verify symptoms grid, FAQ accordion open/close, CTA links
3. Resize to 375px width — verify responsive layout on both pages
4. Click navbar "Teenused" — verify mega-menu shows Webasto link and it navigates correctly

### Manual Verification (user)

1. Deploy to Netlify staging → confirm both pages load at correct URLs
2. Verify FAQ accordion works on mobile (touch)
3. Check form submit snackbar appears
4. Review all Estonian text for correctness
